# .npmignore — the anti-re-leak denylist for `npm publish` (2026-07-11 incident).
# The `files` whitelist ships data/ .thetacog/ docs/ so the demo is self-contained; THIS denies the
# private subset within them so the tarball can never carry it again. Mirror of the mirror-to-public
# denylist. Guarded by tests/ops/npm-pack-no-leak.test.mjs (npm pack must show ZERO private paths).

# ── private telemetry / strategy / personal — NEVER publish ──
.thetacog/cache/
.thetacog/pmu/measurements/
.thetacog/pmu/measure-history/
.thetacog/comms/
.thetacog/blog-mail/
data/pmu/shortlex-children-candidate.json
data/pmu/measure-history.ndjson
data/pmu/measure-history.attestation.json
data/pmu/pipeline/
data/pmu/sigma-localize/
data/pmu/study/
docs/comms/
docs/strategy/
docs/outreach/
docs/research/

# build artifacts / deps
node_modules/
pmu-rust/target/
*.log
.env
.env.*
.DS_Store
